                     <interp inst="t18240916-38-person372" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 21st of July, I received the prisoner in charge from the last witness; the witness charged him with taking a 5 s., in copper. I did not hear what the prisoner said.</p>
